    "description": "The lightmaXX VEGA ZOOM LED Moving Head is an LED moving head with zoom featuring seven 12W RGBW LEDs, a 190° tilt, a 540° pan, and is operable via DMX control, eight auto run programs, and sound-to-light and master-slave. The VEGA OWL is an LED moving head with seven luminous LEDs that deliver a high performance. It is a compact wash/beam moving head with a wide zoom range for small to medium-sized stages or a mobile lightshow.",
